, with a population of about 1,380,100, is the capital city of Nicaragua. Situated on the southwestern shore of Lake Managua, at 12°9'N,86°16'W, 
<REF ID="1109.2" SEMCAT="city" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="common" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="plain">the city</REFEX>
