 is overwhelmingly populated by Spanish-speaking Whites and Mestizos. There are also third, fourth and fifth generation communities of Catalonians, Germans, Italians, and French as well as Middle Easterners. Asians -- entirely Japanese and Chinese (both Mainlanders and Taiwanese) -- recently there has also been a growing number of Americans moving to 
